{"tid":1009941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★冚家Slave】迪士尼樂園鼓勵一家人參與義務工作。完成八小時義務工作，可得到門票一張","createTime":"2019-02-05T14:22:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T05:14:26.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a74f10ae9e09f37f662aa2d9ef8e8584863b1781","tid":1009941,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T14:22:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">迪士尼樂園與義務工作發展局合作推出計劃，鼓勵一家人參與義務工作。</span><br />\n<br />\n迪士尼樂園公布推行「一家義」計劃，計劃邀請十多間服務機構，推動親子義務工作。一個家庭每完成八小時義務工作，便可得到一張樂園門票，最多可獲四張。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5c596a59e60383e9628bb736/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5c596a59e60383e9628bb736%2F&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFuaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=b132b1a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5c596a59e60383e9628bb736/</a>"},{"pid":"8cbc72cbcb2e9b83b4a493b20cd4da78ef4b46be","tid":1009941,"uid":19454,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T14:22:43.000Z","msg":"FREE Slave<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"892a67f3a146e5346053b244e6d861fc7d61857e","tid":1009941,"uid":19454,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T14:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/214850_088e5cbe5691f2e64c2a73a831246722.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F214850_088e5cbe5691f2e64c2a73a831246722.gif&h=8dae661d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97245b49ac69ab54658b357afec078e19927ee5d","tid":1009941,"uid":83060,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T14:24:46.000Z","msg":"綜援家庭年年唔使錢去，做員工仲低賤過咬老綜。"},{"pid":"bb3757e483fa529e56e5104cf36e7af46fab2471","tid":1009941,"uid":164167,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T14:24:50.000Z","msg":"無迫佢地做都叫slave <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm